    "description": {
      "zh": ".300win mag（7.62x67B）空尖弹，采用10.9克铅芯配空心铜尖与黄铜弹壳，专为狩猎及靶场训练打造。该弹种凭借卓越的停止作用在命中目标后能造成严重创伤，甚至可击穿基础防弹护具，所以被定义为大型猎物狩猎弹药。",
      "en": "A .300 Winchester Magnum (7.62x67B) HP cartridge with a 10.9 gram lead core with a hollow copper tip and brass casing; intended for hunting and target practice, This cartridge is intended for use against Big Game as it has an oustanding stopping power effect and is capable of causing severe damage on the target post-impact and can even pierce some rudimentary ballistic armor."
    },
